{"type": "article", "id": 18141, "title": "纸板汽车", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-27T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606003107ZTa2SXnF4cvkQ6Ot.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个给孩子玩的纸板汽车，来自德国一家专业生产儿童玩具的公司 kickpack。它相当于一个小车模型，有可打开的车顶和门窗，是很有情景感的游戏场所。玩累了之后，里面也是睡觉的好地方。材料上使用双层硬纸板制作，是完全可回收的。售价 80 欧元，<a href=\"http://kickpack-shop.de/en/detail/index/sArticle/73\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060031062LiAMXQpo0Nv6KHk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69193154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003106NItKxEUcaoRqlf9b.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69193154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003106nemA9XVwotJalMu5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69193154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060031074N7pLeG8Miy6YfwP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69193154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}